7. Installation & Running Instructions
Step 1 – Install dependencies
pip install pandas numpy
Step 2 – Place input file
Save your CSV in the same folder as:
input_logs.csv
Step 3 – Run the pipeline
python notebook_script.py
Step 4 – View Output
Generated:
output.csv
